{"tid":1655601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"厲害了我的鄰國！量子波動速讀法","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T01:57:40.000Z","uid":216163,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1d12847532f6fd6f31d53188df8529fc4439a439","tid":1655601,"uid":216163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"大陸有人發明了一種閱讀方法叫做「#量子波動速讀法」，聲稱能提升10倍的記憶力，因此吸引了很多家長送孩子去學習。<br />\n<br />\n影片內容顯示，多名青少年用相當快的速度在「翻書」，不過以正常人的閱讀速度，什麼都看不到，有些人重複翻了又翻，不過當中也有「正常的人」，用正常的速度在閱讀，一頁一頁慢慢翻。<br />\n<br />\n其他網友回覆：「果然是活在自己世界的國家」、「既然要翻那麼多次為什麼不一頁頁翻呢？有點浮誇啊小朋友」、「見識到速讀的神奇奧妙了，原來我們真的是井底之蛙」、「第一位小朋友真厲害，知道這樣用書本煽風，現場一定很熱」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">54秒有正妹，正妹就是正常翻閱，其它人在幹嘛</span>」等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MilkBull/videos/961266560919137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMilkBull%2Fvideos%2F961266560919137&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9EzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7eefa568\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MilkBull/videos/961266560919137</a>"},{"pid":"635c8d9503fb3fb62aa189f6805014bf0282f0e0","tid":1655601,"uid":122134,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"識咩<br />\n用潛意識記住<br />\n當你完全唔知自己睇左咩<br />\n就代表你已經記得晒內容<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e23041d605774ff147bf92d8552d167492c771","tid":1655601,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:56:42.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.